{"tid":459856,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯供詞：服務警隊35年　退休前被檢控感痛心","createTime":"2017-11-06T07:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T08:16:32.000Z","uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"999ee6ea17fb289a7ea1c522af652759a788d61d","tid":459856,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"退休警司朱經緯涉嫌在2014年佔領行動期間，在旺角以警棍打途人的案件，下午繼續在東區裁判法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n根據朱經緯在警方警誡下錄取的書面供詞指，在臨近退休前面對檢控，感到痛心；又說自己服務警隊35年，真心認為是根據條例行使法定權力。<br />\n<br />\n朱經緯表示案發時他要保護自己，防止罪案發生，當時有人嘗試衝破警方防線，他的做法是別無選擇。他又說，相關片段不能真實反映當時發生暴力的情況。"},{"pid":"0c91ba8057c6060e7fdd5ed19c06494500d71221","tid":459856,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"36!9"},{"pid":"29e126bf37a12d6964f66b762d6087adc7a00619","tid":459856,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bad6224318fe5a28d20db2cd667184a4aafb60c","tid":459856,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"判左啦？"},{"pid":"c3d57350cb9c0f016c75e48a4b04977d6b3dec37","tid":459856,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"賤種，始終都係賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c39d64e4d49848b6c4e8eb911e1f23cf5e60ae","tid":459856,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵<br />\n撚<br />\n死<br />\n！</span>"},{"pid":"a515192be9ff73ec643bb5259e133b40e8e5943d","tid":459856,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"他又說，相關片段不能真實反映當時發生暴力的情況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7374dd96582887cd4fff1b33a414